me with them. It wasn't because he was a loser, and it definitely wasn't because he was gay. The only reason people kept saying so was because one of the assholes on the hockey team started a rumor about it back in high school. Based on nothing! It was just because Whit was small, and preferred art over sports, and because those stupid jocks all had brain damage from slamming their thick heads into the ice all the time. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Sometimes Whit wondered if that rumor would've died down if he hadn't reacted so aggressively whenever someone brought it up. It had led to a lot of fights over the years, fights that usually ended up with one of the hockey jerks cramming his frail little body into a locker while the rest of them watched and laughed. Fuck them. You couldn't let people walk all over you like that. They had challenged Whit’s masculinity, and Whit never backed down from a challenge.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Not even a “try not to cum” challenge.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Oh, god… that feels so good…”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Horny moans rang out over his crappy laptop speakers. Whit hunched over the laptop, masturbating furiously. On the screen, a young woman writhed and moaned in ecstasy as she played with herself. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The girl in the video was a picture of perfect feminine innocence, from her bouncing pigtails to her cute little knee-high socks. She looked like a fresh-faced college student, pleasuring herself to relax after a long, hard day of studying. Only most college girls didn't have such a professional camera set up… or such a long, thick cock. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Oh, I'm gonna cum… I'm gonna cum so hard... Oooh…”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Whit’s hand jerked rapidly under his desk, tugging back and forth on his own slick cock. God, this video was so hot. The girl’s pretty face, her soft little body, the pleading look in her eyes. Everything about her screamed “submissive slut”. Sure, right now she was just playing with herself, but what would she do