&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“That's the type of person you are now?” Whit squeaked. Fuck! He gritted his teeth and jabbed a finger at the door, “Get the fuck out of my room, Varun.”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Bug–”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“And don't fucking call me that! Fuck off to the rest of your fucking Neanderthal hockey bros, you fucking normie idiot! God!”&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Whit shoved Varun out of his room, ignoring his protests, then slammed the door behind him. He flopped down onto his chair with a frustrated hiss. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Fucking traitor. I it wasn’t clear enough already, that confirmed it. His best friend from high school was fucking dead. Whit heard the front door slam as Varun headed out. Good riddance. From now on, Whit didn’t want anything to do with Varun Sharma.He rolled his chair back to his desk and opened his laptop. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The porn window was still open, frozen on the final frame of the video he had been watching. The sissy girl lay sprawled on her bed, splattered with her own cum, smiling blissfully. Whit grimaced. God, he was pathetic. Sitting at home, jerking off to sissy porn. Maybe the guys on the hockey team were right. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;He scowled. No. Fuck them. He wasn't fucking gay, alright? The title of the video literally said “girl” in it, that was the only reason he had watched it. He nodded to himself, growing more convinced in his argument. Yeah, the title said “girl”, and the thumbnail was a pretty girl with pigtails, how was he supposed to know that she had a dick? It was false advertising, honestly. He had been tricked. He wasn't the sick one, it was the girl – no, the &lt;em&gt;guy&lt;/em&gt; – in the video who was sick.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Someone should teach him a fucking lesson.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Whit smirked and started typing out a comment. He made sure to include all his complaints. The video was sick and perverted and wrong, the title was misleading (he ignored the part of the title that mentioned the star having a dick), the sissy wasn't even hot, cumming that fast was completely pathetic, anyone who watched this sort of thing was a total loser… the list went on. Whit gained confidence as he typed. Yeah, this would show that sissy freak who was boss. He glanced back up at the video and scowled again. Fucking pervert, looking so satisfied and comfortable, lying back on her bed with her soft tan skin splattered with pearly globs of her splooge. How dare she be so happy!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Whit finished his comment and looked back over it again. Excellent work. He had made some very cutting remarks and showed off his impressive vocabulary and sharp critical mind. Was there anything missing? The girl in the video looked to be Latina, should he say something about that? Whit bit his lip. No, he wasn't racist, and that reminded him uncomfortably of some of the things the hockey guys used to say to Varun. He wouldn't stoop to that level. Instead, he added a few more homophobic slurs, gave the comment one last read-through to check for typos, and then posted it with a satisfied grin. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The website gave the option to like or dislike comments, and Whit was sure this one would get a lot of likes. His comments usually did, which made sense because he was so smart and insightful. He liked his own comment, then switched over to Reddit to browse for a bit. Ooh, someone had posted a stupid question on a gaming subreddit. His skills were needed again already.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;A few hours later, Whit had thoroughly demolished a whole bunch of ignorant fools on Reddit and was feeling much better about himself. At some point he had heard Varun come back home, but fortunately he kept to himself this time. Whit stretched and yawned. It was probably time for bed, it had been a big day. Hmm. Maybe a quick jack session first. He flicked back over to his porn tab and scrolled down to see how many likes his comment had accrued.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Negative twelve.&lt;/p&gt; &l